{
  "stem": "22910.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I never went to fourth grade, and I never learned long division.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] And you'd be surprised for how long-- and I was very good in math.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was my favorite subject.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For how long the fact that I didn't learn long division made a difference.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I went to the fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, that was it, because that was already-- the war started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war started.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to the Czech school closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember, a Shabbat morning, we got up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was called-- was-- was recruited to the army, because a war started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think a few days later, they came back, and Czechoslovakia was simply dismembered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at first, the Ukrainians took over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was really bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- it was dangerous for my grandfather, because they said, now we're going to take everything away from you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, you're you're not going to live like you were used to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And just within a few months, the Hungarians came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's when things started to be bad really, because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, being in a small town, there's no newspaper and certainly not a town radio or something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were very few people who had radios.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the way they used to disseminate news, like all kinds of laws, new laws-- I don't, know maybe in movies you saw, where they'd come to a village-- it was a town, not a village-- to the square with a drum.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bum, bum, bum, bum, bum, bum, bum, you know, calling everybody together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they'd read off the new laws or anything new.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they'd go to different squares like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this how we found out about anything new.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
